  "title": "Gardener (FT and PT)",
  "description": "<p><strong>🌿 Join Our Landscaping Team! 🌿</strong></p><p>Are you passionate about working outdoors and bringing landscapes to life? We're hiring dedicated <strong>landscape maintenance crew members (Full Time and Part Time)</strong> to help us create and maintain beautiful green spaces!</p><h3><strong>Responsibilities:</strong></h3><p>✅ Weeding and mulching landscape beds<br />✅ Trimming small trees, hedges, and shrubs<br />✅ Removing dead or unwanted plants<br />✅ Planting shrubs and flowers<br />✅ Watering gardens, lawns, and landscapes<br />✅ Grass cutting and lawn care<br />✅ Fertilizing plants for healthy growth<br />✅ Monitoring and maintaining plant health</p><h3><strong>What We’re Looking For:</strong></h3><p>🌱 Hardworking and reliable individuals<br />🌱 Ability to work outdoors in various weather conditions<br />🌱 Previous landscaping experience is a plus but not required<br />🌱 Willingness to learn and work as part of a team</p><h3><strong>Why Join Us?</strong></h3><p>🌳 Competitive pay<br />🌳 Friendly and supportive team<br />🌳 Opportunities to grow and develop your skills<br />🌳 Work in beautiful outdoor environments</p>",
