    "description": "<p>OneO2Plants PTE. LTD.</p>\n<p>Established in 2008, OneO2Plants is a subsidiary of Far East Flora – an integrated floriculture firm with over 40 years of experience. We endeavor to bring life and freshness to the space of every business in Asia by making our extensive range of plants and pots available for rent in your office space.</p>\n<p>With our wide variety of plants and European pot designs, OneO2Plants can provide the options and service level you require. We are able to provide plant rental for offices, restaurants, hotels, commercial buildings, shopping malls, and events. Our rapidly growing clientele in Singapore can attest to our quality service, enthusiasm and reliability. With renewable annual rental contracts, our plant nurturers will visit your premises every fortnightly to ensure that your plants stay healthy and fresh throughout the year.</p>\n<p>Our other services also include plants for events, plants for purchase and floral arrangements. Whichever service you require, you can be assured that customer satisfaction is our number one priority.</p>",
